Package: rtomahawk
Type: Package
Title: Tools for computing, querying and storing linkage-disequilibrium data
Version: 1.0
Date: 2018-12-17
Author: Marcus D. R. Klarqvist
Maintainer: Marcus D. R. Klarqvist <mk819@cam.ac.uk>
Description: Tomahawk is a unified framework for computing, storing, querying, aggregating, and plotting genome-wide linkage-disequilibrium (LD) data in population-scaled cohorts. This package is an R interface to Tomahawk
License: MIT
URL: https://github.com/mklarqvist/tomahawk
BugReports: https://github.com/mklarqvist/tomahawk/issues
